Tng quan gia cc bin s v percent_change (Bin ng gi SSI)

  • buy: Tng quan dng (0.317) vi percent_change. Cho thy khi s lng "buy" tng, gi c phiu SSI c xu hng tng. iu ny c th xem xt l mt tn hiu tch cc cho vic mua vo khi ch s "buy" cao.

  • sell: Tng quan m mnh (-0.488) vi percent_change. Khi s lng "sell" tng, gi c phiu SSI c xu hng gim. y l mt tn hiu xem xt bn ra khi ch s "sell" tng cao.

  • waitbuy: Tng quan yu (0.048) vi percent_change. Ch s "waitbuy" dng nh khng c mi quan h mnh vi bin ng gi SSI, do c th t c s dng trong quyt nh giao dch.

  • waitsell: Tng quan dng yu (0.087), tuy nhin khi xem xt tng quan gia waitsell v percent_change thp, nhng waitsell li c tng quan m vi waitbuy (-0.497), cho thy khi ch s "waitsell" tng, gi c phiu c th khng tng nhiu hoc c xu hng gim.

Nhn xt tng quan gia cc thng s buy, sell, waitbuy, waitsell

  • buy v sell: -0.2907. Cho thy khi tn hiu mua (buy) tng ln, tn hiu bn (sell) c xu hng gim. Mi tng quan m ny hp l v khi nhiu ngi mua vo, s lng ngi bn ra thng gim.

  • buy v waitbuy: 0.3746. Cho thy s tng quan dng kh mnh, cho thy rng khi tn hiu ch mua (waitbuy) tng, tn hiu mua (buy) cng c xu hng tng. iu ny c th gii thch l khi c nhiu tn hiu ch mua, cc nh u t c xu hng chuyn sang hnh ng mua thc s.

  • buy v waitsell: -0.2224. y l mt mi tng quan m, cho thy rng khi tn hiu ch bn (waitsell) tng, tn hiu mua (buy) c xu hng gim. iu ny hp l v khi nhiu ngi ch bn, s lng ngi mua c th gim i.

  • sell v waitbuy: -0.0804. Tng quan m kh nh, cho thy rng khi tn hiu ch mua (waitbuy) tng, tn hiu bn (sell) c xu hng gim nh. Tuy nhin, do mi tng quan ny kh yu, s nh hng gia hai bin s khng qu r rng.

  • sell v waitsell: 0.1067. y l mt mi tng quan dng yu, cho thy rng khi tn hiu ch bn (waitsell) tng, tn hiu bn (sell) cng c xu hng tng. iu ny hp l v khi nhiu ngi ch bn, c th dn n vic nhiu ngi thc s bn ra.

  • waitbuy v waitsell: -0.4971. y l mt mi tng quan m mnh, cho thy rng khi tn hiu ch mua (waitbuy) tng, tn hiu ch bn (waitsell) c xu hng gim r rt. iu ny hp l v khi nhiu ngi ang ch mua, s lng ngi ch bn c th gim i.

3. Thut ton

S dng thut ton Kmean phn vng cc gi tr ca 4 ch s (buy, sell, waitbuy, waitsell) d on khi no nn mua vo hay bn ra c phiu SSI.

In[19]:
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler


data = df[['buy', 'sell', 'waitsell', 'waitbuy']]

# Chun ha d liu
scaler = StandardScaler()
data_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(data)

# S dng phng php Elbow  tm K ti u
wcss = []
for i in range(1, 20):
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=i, init='k-means++', random_state=42)
    kmeans.fit(data_scaled)
    wcss.append(kmeans.inertia_)

plt.plot(range(1, 20), wcss)
plt.title('Elbow Method')
plt.xlabel('Number of clusters')
plt.ylabel('WCSS')
plt.show()

# Chn K = 4 da trn biu  Elbow 
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=4, init='k-means++', random_state=42)
y_kmeans = kmeans.fit_predict(data_scaled)

# Gn nhn cm vo df
df['cluster'] = y_kmeans

print(df.head())

Nhn xt

  • Cm 0: sell thp tp trung nhiu gi tr 0 - 20, cn buy cao tp trung nhiu trong khong 10 - 100, waitbuy cao tp trung nhiu t 50 - 200, ngc li waitsell thp ch t 10 - 80
  • Cm 1: sell tp trung nhiu trong khong 0 - 40, buy tp trung trong khong 0 -40, nhng waitsell tp trung nhiu trong khong 100 - 200, waitbuy ch t 0 - 90
  • Cm 2: sell tp trung nhiu trong khong 0 - 40, buy tp trung trong khong 0 -40, nhng waitbuy tp trung nhiu trong khong 10 - 150, waitsell tp trung nhiu khong 10 - 100
  • Cm 3: sell cao tp trung nhiu trong khong 40 - 120, trong khi buy thp tp trung nhiu trong khong 0 - 20, waitsell, waitbuy gi tr tri di phn b rng chng t nh hng khng ng k

Nhn xt vng gi tr v c im ca tng cm, t em c tn cho tng cm nh sau:

  • Cm 0: "Mua Mnh - Bn Yu"
    Sell thp: Tp trung nhiu gi tr t 0 - 20.
    Buy cao: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 10 - 100.
    Waitbuy cao: Tp trung nhiu t 50 - 200.
    Waitsell thp: Ch t 10 - 80.
    Cm ny c cc c im cho thy hot ng mua vo (buy) mnh m, trong khi bn ra (sell) yu, waitbuy cao chng t s k vng mua vo ln, v waitsell thp cho thy t p lc bn ra.

  • Cm 1: "Ch Bn - Mua Yu"
    Sell tp trung: Trong khong 0 - 40.
    Buy tp trung: Trong khong 0 - 40.
    Waitsell cao: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 100 - 200.
    Waitbuy thp: Ch t 0 - 90.
    Cm ny c xu hng ch i bn ra vi waitsell cao, trong khi mua vo (buy) kh yu v waitbuy thp, cho thy t mong i v s tng gi.

  • Cm 2: "Ch C Hi - Th Trng Bnh n"
    Sell tp trung: Trong khong 0 - 40.
    Buy tp trung: Trong khong 0 - 40.
    Waitbuy trung bnh: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 10 - 150.
    Waitsell trung bnh: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 10 - 100.
    Cm ny cho thy th trng n nh vi c hai ch s waitbuy v waitsell u mc trung bnh, th hin s ch i c hi m khng c hnh ng mnh m t pha nh u t.

  • Cm 3: "Bn Mnh - Mua Yu"
    Sell cao: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 40 - 120.
    Buy thp: Tp trung nhiu trong khong 0 - 20.
    Waitsell, waitbuy tri di: Gi tr phn b rng, nh hng khng ng k.
    Cm ny cho thy hot ng bn ra mnh m vi ch s sell cao, trong khi mua vo (buy) yu, waitsell, waitbuy tri di khng c xu hng r rng.

cluster_names = {
    0: 'Mua Mnh - Bn Yu',
    1: 'Ch Bn - Mua Yu',
    2: 'Ch C Hi - Th Trng Bnh n',
    3: 'Bn Mnh - Mua Yu'
}

# Hm d on 
def predict_cluster(buy, sell, waitbuy, waitsell):
    
    new_data = pd.DataFrame([[buy, sell, waitsell, waitbuy]], columns=['buy', 'sell', 'waitsell', 'waitbuy'])
    
    new_data_scaled = scaler.transform(new_data)
    
    cluster = kmeans.predict(new_data_scaled)[0]
  
    return cluster_names[cluster]

# V d: D on cm cho mt im d liu mi nh sau:
new_buy = 100
new_sell = 10
new_waitbuy = 100
new_waitsell = 20

predicted_cluster = predict_cluster(new_buy, new_sell, new_waitbuy, new_waitsell)
print(f'Vi im d liu ny bn nn: {predicted_cluster}')

Vi im d liu ny bn nn: Mua Mnh - Bn Yu

S dng Logistic Regression v Random Forest d bo v ti u ha chin lc giao dch cho c phiu SSI trong ngy

In[23]:
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler

# Gi s bin mc tiu l `target` (v d: nu `percent_change` > 0 th 1 ngha l gi tng, ngc li 0 ngha l gi gim)
df['target'] = (df['percent_change'] > 0).astype(int)

# Chn cc bin c trng
features = ['buy', 'sell', 'waitbuy', 'waitsell']
X = df[features]
y = df['target']

# Chia d liu thnh tp hun luyn v tp kim tra
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.3, random_state=42)

# Chun ha d liu
scaler = StandardScaler()
X_train_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X_train)
X_test_scaled = scaler.transform(X_test)
In[24]:
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, accuracy_score

# To m hnh Logistic Regression
logreg = LogisticRegression()
logreg.fit(X_train_scaled, y_train)

# D on trn tp kim tra
y_pred_logreg = logreg.predict(X_test_scaled)

print("Logistic Regression Classification Report:")
print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred_logreg))
print(f"Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred_logreg)}")

# Da trn d on ca m hnh, c th ti u ha chin lc giao dch.
# V d: nu xc sut tng gi (d on) > 0.5, c th quyt nh mua vo.

# D on xc sut vi Logistic Regression v Random Forest 
y_prob_logreg = logreg.predict_proba(X_test_scaled)[:, 1]

y_prob_rf = rf.predict_proba(X_test_scaled)[:, 1]

# V d: Quyt nh mua vo nu xc sut d on ca Logistic Regression > 0.5
buy_signal_logreg = y_prob_logreg > 0.5
buy_signal_rf = y_prob_rf > 0.5

print("Logistic Regression Buy Signal:")
print(buy_signal_logreg)

print("Random Forest Buy Signal:")
print(buy_signal_rf)
